Drupal 8 issues
1.Installation issues
- on installation getting error on xdebug
add the following line at the end of xdebug in php.ini
xdebug.max_nesting_level = 256
- increase the maximum execution time to 500
- enable the mod rewrite in php.ini and restart the apache.

